quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  94,1,Kon na Kamoe plah roe dada gata
  94,2,Kamoe cok dacha teuh meu na salah
  94,3,Mangat bek geuhon gata meularat
  94,4,Lom meubri pangkat teuh manyang leupah
  94,5,Keubit meu susah awai meularat Bak akhe meuhat seunang ngon mudah
  94,6,Bit meunyo susah awai meularat Bak akhe meuhat seunang ngon mudah
  94,7,Teuma ‘oh lheuh tapubuet ibadat Usaha ligat ngon susah payah
  94,8,Ubak Po gata taingat ligat Beu keubit that-that cinta keu Allah